You can match most bands with any Apple Watch Series 3 or newer case of the same size. The 41mm bands work with 38mm and 40mm cases; the 45mm bands work with 42mm and 44mm cases.

name: Nike Force 1 LV8 2
product_details:
From the court to the crib, the Air Force 1 is a legend—no matter your generation. This kids' version of the AF1 can be worn anywhere, and best of all, they go with almost any outfit. Built like the original with durable leather, we added a bit more to this edition: Glossy, silky textures up your little one's sneaker game, worthy of showing off for playtime and of course, baby pictures!


Heritage Style

Real and synthetic leather makes these shoes durable—just like the old-school Air Force 1 first released in '82.


Built to Last

A full rubber sole gives durable traction. Fun fact: The circular tread pattern was originally used to help basketball players pivot on the court.


Cushioned Comfort

Soft foam on the collar and tongue provides extra cushioning around the ankles.


Product Details

  • Classic laces
  • Shown: Monarch/Sail
  • Style: DX1886-800

name: Nike Air Force 1 ’07 LX
product_details:
Take your love for the game with you wherever you go. Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, these kicks put a fresh spin on a hoops classic with washed-out neon colors and classic paisley print. Of course, we kept the same era-echoing '80s construction and hidden Nike Air units you know and love for that legendary AF1 feel. Go ahead, slip into a slam dunk.


Benefits

  • From tough stitching to pristine materials to the cupsole design, these sneakers deliver durable style that’s smoother than backboard glass.
  • Originally designed for performance hoops, Nike Air cushioning delivers lasting comfort.
  • Low-cut, padded collar looks sleek and feels great.
  • Rubber outsole with heritage hoops pivot circles adds traction and durability.
  • Shown: White/White/Mint Foam/Phantom
  • Style: FJ7739-101

Air Force 1

Debuting in 1982 as a basketball must-have, the Air Force 1 came into its own in the '90s. The clean look of the classic white-on-white AF1 was endorsed from the basketball courts to the block and beyond. Finding its rhythm in hip-hop culture, releasing limited collabs and colorways, Air Force 1 became an iconic sneaker around the globe. And with over 2000 iterations of this staple, its impact on fashion, music and sneaker culture can’t be denied.

name: Paris Saint-Germain 2023/24 Match Home
sub_title: Men's Nike Dri-FIT ADV Soccer Jersey
product_details:
The inspiration for the PSG 2023/24 Home kit comes from La Ville Lumiere ("City of Light"). The mostly blue jersey has an off-center red graphic fading to blue, mimicking the way the iconic lights of Paris fade into the night sky. A hidden design inside has the team name, while outer details feature the French flag. Our Match collection pairs authentic design details with lightweight, quick-drying technology to help keep the world’s biggest soccer stars cool and comfortable on the field.


Benefits

  • Nike Dri-FIT ADV technology combines moisture-wicking fabric with advanced engineering and features to help you stay dry and comfortable.
  • Informed by athlete testing, open-hole fabric in high-heat zones helps you stay cool when the game heats up.
  • Authentic design is the same look worn by the pros on the field.

Product Details

  • 100% polyester
  • Machine wash
  • Imported
  • Shown: Midnight Navy/University Red/University Red
  • Style: DX2620-411
